      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON GYPSY (1) has a strong record here with four wins and two placings from eight starts. Was out of placings last time (29.72) at this track in a OPEN, finishing fourth and beaten 3 lengths. Looks a leading chance on best. COMPTON GOLD (3) found some support last start but struggled into fourth (29.72), beaten 5 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Has good speed and a low draw is a big help. Worth following up. BELAIR LAUREL (6) turned in a modest effort most recently when eighth at The Meadows over 525m behind Analyzation (30.97) in a Grade 5 FIN. Was a winner prior to that. The form from her last run stacks up well. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. HONEY ZEN (8) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
